🎙️ What happens when an AI builder becomes a storyteller? What if the machine isn’t the real experiment — we are?
In the next episode of The Adycted Show, we sit down with Yogesh — Senior Product Manager at Google DeepMind and the author of a deeply introspective sci-fi novel: The Final Experiment.
But this episode isn’t just about AI, books, or career journeys. It’s about reinvention. Reflection. And asking the harder questions we usually avoid.
Here’s what we explore:
✨ How curiosity led him from telecom to DeepMind to fiction
✨ The story behind The Final Experiment — and what it says about identity, memory, and control
✨ How fiction sometimes tells the truth better than facts ever could
If you’ve ever felt like you’re more than one thing…
If you’ve ever questioned the system while working inside it…
If you’re building the future but want to stay human while doing it —
This one’s for you.
📌 Teaser out now. Full episode on 11 July 2025.
